		  <div class="panel-body">
		  		<div class="col-lg-12">
                  	<div class="progress" style="margin-bottom:8px;">
					  <div class="progress-bar" style="width: 50%;"></div>
					</div>
					 <p>请对您的咨询者进行评分，客观公正的评分对您,点击
